Hello peers. I got an issue while Calling Extension SDK events .Why the calling extension sdk onReady event giving *engagementId*: undefined
*iframeLocation:* undefined
*ownerId* undefined
*portalId* 48660576
*userId:* 0

I want the userId with onReady event . I am integrating my custom IFRAME in HubSpot calling . Actually I am using a free developer account. Within that I created a test account . When I tried making a call from a contact in contact pages in test Account I got userId 0 as payload from HubSpot's onReady event.
If it is not possible to get userId through onReady event in free account , is there any chance that I can get the correct userId in the payload of onReady event if I purchase a paid one ?
